media:group.media:title: Splatoon Island - Announcement Trailer
media:group.media:description:
GENRE: Game/April Fools

Based on the game series "Splatoon" by Nintendo

Inklings are bringing their ink to the next level. Now with the dangers of water!
Splatoon Island is a mobile game full of mini-games set on a vacation island. Who says adult Inklings can't have extreme fun?

Coming soon in early April 3020.

Play the fake game (sort of) on Gamejolt:
https://gamejolt.com/games/splatoonisland/406234
